"Test | y & con vectores y matrices
'<hr/>
"1. | escalar (ya funcionaba)
L = 6*m
L|cm
L|mm

'<hr/>
"2. | [vector] — conversión por elemento
u = [0.001*m; 0.0005*m; 0.002*rad]
u
u | [cm; cm; rad]
u | [mm; mm; rad]

'<hr/>
"3. & [vector] — adimensionalizar + stamp
E = 2100000*kgf/cm^2
A = 100*cm^2
I = 5000*cm^4
Lv = 400*cm
k1 = E*A/Lv
k2 = 12*E*I/Lv^3
k3 = 6*E*I/Lv^2
k4 = 4*E*I/Lv
K = [k1; 0*kgf/cm; 0*kgf | 0*kgf/cm; k2; k3 | 0*kgf; k3; k4]

'F calculado para u=[0.1cm, 0.05cm, 0.001rad]:
F1 = k1*0.1*cm
F2 = k2*0.05*cm + k3*0.001
F3 = k3*0.05*cm + k4*0.001
Fv = [F1; F2; F3]

'<h4>lsolve con & [cm; cm; rad]</h4>
u_sol = lsolve(K; Fv) & [cm; cm; rad]
u_sol

'<h4>Mismo resultado con | [cm; cm; rad]</h4>
u_raw = lsolve(K; Fv)
u_raw | [cm; cm; rad]

'<hr/>
"4. | [matriz] — conversión por celda
K2 = [100*kN/m; 50*kN | 50*kN; 200*kN*m]
K2
K2 | [tonf/m; tonf | tonf; tonf*m]
